No. 09-939. Kenneth Derek Anthony Pillay, Petitioner v. Cisco Systems, Inc., et al. 559 U.S. 1086, 130 S. Ct. 2098,

176 L. Ed. 2d 756,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3246. April 19, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Justice Breyer took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
